step 1:
-> Open Conda Powershell
-> create virtual environemnt using following command
  -> conda create -n environemnt_name python==3.7
  
 step 2:
-> Create any folder at any location and copy that folder_location_path 
-> open conda powershell/ Terminal and use following command to set path
  -> cd folder_location_path

step 3:
activate virtual environemnt
  -> conda activate environemnt_name

step 4:
Install Rasa using command:
  -> install rasa --extra-index-url https://pypi.rasa.com/simple
  # if you face any problem then first downgrade your pip version
  -> pip install --upgrade pip==20.2
  # now run above command

step 5:
Run follwing command:
  -> rasa init
  -> rasa train
  -> rasa shell # after retraing model
  


For Rasa-X Installation:

just change minor change in step:4 as following
step 4:
Install Rasa-X using command:
  -> install rasa-X --extra-index-url https://pypi.rasa.com/simple
  # if you face any problem then first downgrade your pip version
  -> pip install --upgrade pip==20.2
  # now run above command




If you face Rasa-X error use this command:

 -> pip install rasa-x==0.26.3 --extra-index-url https://pypi.rasa.com/simple



